      "detailed": "Incident INC-231 (see ops/incident.md): a customer clicked buy ONCE for two WIDGET-9, was charged twice, and stock dropped 5 -> 1. Using the captured logs in ops/logs/ and the service code, trace what happened across the services and report the root cause chain: which configured value set it off, which behavior amplified it, and what the customer-visible + inventory effects were. INVESTIGATION ONLY — do NOT modify any files; report your diagnosis."
