      "detailed": "You are on call. Work incident INC-407 (brief in ops/INC-407.md): during the 2026-07-01 morning traffic ramp, checkouts failed with 502s and several customers got DOUBLE pending charges for one purchase attempt. Production logs, deploy history, config history, and metrics are only available through the cloud CLI at ./ops/cloudctl (start with `./ops/cloudctl help`). Establish the full root-cause chain: what change set the incident up, what conditions triggered it, how the failure propagated across services, and what produced the duplicate charges. Cite the specific deploy and configuration involved. INVESTIGATION ONLY — do NOT modify any files; report your diagnosis."
