    "note": "HARD investigation: evidence lives behind a mock cloud CLI over ~5k log lines in gzipped shards + deploy/config/metric stores, with planted red herrings (slow analytics queries, cold-cache warns, an innocent deploy, a self-resolved webhook burst). Root cause: deploy d-9182 cut the payments connection pool 16→4; the traffic ramp exhausted it; charge latency blew orders' 300ms deadline; the gateway's non-idempotent retry double-charged."
